        <Parent_String>Renaissance-Baroque ceramics styles [300021168], Renaissance-Baroque decorative arts styles [300021164], Renaissance-Baroque styles [300021033], Renaissance-Baroque styles and periods [300021031], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
